description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated and committed Nurse Team Leader to join our friendly and supportive team to work on 7A.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7A is a 29 bedded ward specialising in Vascular Surgery. We provide a variety of diverse and complex treatment to vascular patients. The ward will be the vascular hub for the area and will incorporate 6 monitored beds which will ensure our patients no longer require HDU post surgery. We are committed to providing the best care possible to all patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is suitable for Band 5 with at least 2 years experience in vascular and general surgery. Applicants must demonstrate excellent leadership and communication skills on a day to day basis to lead the team. The successful applicant must deputise for the senior sister.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer various training that will enhance your leadership skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will require participation on weekends, bank holidays, nights and rotational duties for 24 hour nursing cover.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward Manager Mandy Sims on 01438 28 5714.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E-mail- mandysims@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
